{"tid":1833903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭 : 我辭職只會帶來不穩和混亂","createTime":"2020-01-22T06:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T11:49:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":215,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb6f4efccc8e93bd7c0b21bb2d115d96fe2e8b9","tid":1833903,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/CNBC-CE-200122-14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FCNBC-CE-200122-14.jpg&h=859389af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】正在瑞士的行政長官林鄭月娥接受多間外國傳媒專訪，指中央希望香港在一國兩制下成功，否認北京收緊對香港管治，又指辭職只會引來不穩定因素，自己有責任確保香港向前行。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在瑞士出席世界經濟論壇年會，接受美國財經頻道CNBC專訪，她對評級機構穆迪下調香港信貸評級感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，監警會正調查警隊處理示威的情況，而警方至今處理多場示威，無人因警方的行動而死亡，反指世界各地都有暴亂，認為國際傳媒不合比例地報道香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n至於她本人的去留，她認為辭職只會增加不穩定因素。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林鄭月娥接受彭博社專訪指，中央並無收緊對香港的管治，認為外間指控失實，強調中央多次清楚表明希望香港在一國兩制、高度自治下取得成功；而國家主席習近平近期與她三次會面，都清楚表明這一點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377711&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=6bbae8f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377711&h=ac3a1fb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377711</a>"},{"pid":"480d752636bf48c4a31969c267e939f1faa46987","tid":1833903,"uid":31254,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"共匪講嘅嘢掉轉睇就係正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59f282438e2e26f4c323e1c7a150d9181435f6d","tid":1833903,"uid":143241,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"過去嗰7個月好歌舞昇平？"},{"pid":"4b633f415c0b1113c08b4e1f8fed645e07ef4e26","tid":1833903,"uid":1